name: Web Onboarding DK - Danish Contents-Accident-Travel With Autocomplete

passages.name: name
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[errorCoInsured]]"
          when="coInsured > 6"
>
</Redirect>

<Message>
  {DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_NAME_MESSAGE_1}
</Message>

<TextActionSet next="[[{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_CONTINUE}->birthDate]]">
  <TextAction title="{DK_CONTENT_NAME_TEXT_ACTION_TITLE_FIRST_NAME}"
              placeholder="{DK_CONTENT_NAME_TEXT_ACTION_PLACEHOLDER_FIRST_NAME}"
              large="true"
              key="firstName"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="{DK_CONTENT_NAME_TEXT_ACTION_TITLE_SURNAME}"
              placeholder="{DK_CONTENT_NAME_TEXT_ACTION_PLACEHOLDER_SURNAME}"
              large="true"
              key="lastName"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: studentEligibilityCheck
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[Offer]]"
          when="birthDate.Age > 30 || livingSpace > 100 || coInsured > 1"
          key="isStudent"
          value="false"
>
</Redirect>

<Redirect to="[[student]]"
          when="true"
>
</Redirect>

passages.name: addressManual
passages.text:
<Track name="AddressNotFound"
       keys="[addressSearchTerm]"
>
</Track>

<Message>
  {ADDRESS_AUTOCOMPLETE_NOT_FOUND_APOLOGY}
</Message>

<Message>
  {ADDRESS_AUTOCOMPLETE_NOT_FOUND_PROMPT}
</Message>

<Response>
  {street}, {zipCode}
</Response>

<TextActionSet next="[[{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_CONTINUE}->addressManualTrack]]">
  <TextAction title="{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_ADDRESS_TEXT_ACTION_TITLE_ADDRESS}"
              placeholder="{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_ADDRESS_PLACEHOLDER}"
              large="true"
              key="street"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_ADDRESS_TEXT_ACTION_TITLE_ZIP_CODE}"
              mask="NorwegianPostalCode"
              placeholder="{DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_ZIP_CODE_PLACEHOLDER}"
              key="zipCode"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: Offer
passages.text:
<Message>
  {DK_CONTENT_CONVERSATION_OFFER_MESSAGE_1}
</Message>

<GraphQLApi next="[[OfferSuccess]]">
  <Mutation>
    mutation CreateDanishQuote(
  $danishHomeContentsQuoteId: ID!
  $danishAccidentQuoteId: ID!
  $danishTravelQuoteId: ID!
  $firstName: String!
  $lastName: String!
  $birthDate: LocalDate!
  $email: String!
  $coInsured: Int!
  $livingSpace: Int!
  $street: String!
  $zipCode: String!
  $type: DanishHomeContentsType!
  $isStudent: Boolean!
  $bbrId: String
  $city: String
  $floor: String
  $apartment: String
) {
  createDanishHomeContentsQuote: createQuote(
    input: {
      id: $danishHomeContentsQuoteId
      firstName: $firstName
      lastName: $lastName
      birthDate: $birthDate
      email: $email
      danishHomeContents: {
        coInsured: $coInsured
        livingSpace: $livingSpace
        street: $street
        zipCode: $zipCode
        type: $type
        isStudent: $isStudent
        bbrId: $bbrId
        city: $city
        floor: $floor
        apartment: $apartment
      }
    }
  ) {
    ... on CompleteQuote {
      id
      insuranceCost {
        monthlyGross {
          amount
          currency
        }
        monthlyDiscount {
          amount
          currency
        }
        monthlyNet {
          amount
          currency
        }
      }
    }
  }
  createDanishAccidentQuote: createQuote(
    input: {
      id: $danishAccidentQuoteId
      firstName: $firstName
      lastName: $lastName
      birthDate: $birthDate
      email: $email
      danishAccident: {
        coInsured: $coInsured
        street: $street
        zipCode: $zipCode
        isStudent: $isStudent
        bbrId: $bbrId
        city: $city
        floor: $floor
        apartment: $apartment
      }
    }
  ) {
    ... on CompleteQuote {
      id
      insuranceCost {
        monthlyGross {
          amount
          currency
        }
        monthlyDiscount {
          amount
          currency
        }
        monthlyNet {
          amount
          currency
        }
      }
    }
  }
  createDanishTravelQuote: createQuote(
    input: {
      id: $danishTravelQuoteId
      firstName: $firstName
      lastName: $lastName
      birthDate: $birthDate
      email: $email
      danishTravel: {
        coInsured: $coInsured
        street: $street
        zipCode: $zipCode
        isStudent: $isStudent
        bbrId: $bbrId
        city: $city
        floor: $floor
        apartment: $apartment
      }
    }
  ) {
    ... on CompleteQuote {
      id
      insuranceCost {
        monthlyGross {
          amount
          currency
        }
        monthlyDiscount {
          amount
          currency
        }
        monthlyNet {
          amount
          currency
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
  </Mutation>
  <GeneratedVariable key="danishHomeContentsQuoteId"
                     type="uuid"
                     storeas="danishHomeContentsQuoteId"
  >
  </GeneratedVariable>
  <GeneratedVariable key="danishAccidentQuoteId"
                     type="uuid"
                     storeas="danishAccidentQuoteId"
  >
  </GeneratedVariable>
  <GeneratedVariable key="danishTravelQuoteId"
                     type="uuid"
                     storeas="danishTravelQuoteId"
  >
  </GeneratedVariable>
  <Variable key="firstName"
            from="firstName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="lastName"
            from="lastName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="birthDate"
            from="birthDate"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="email"
            from="email"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="coInsured"
            from="coInsured"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="livingSpace"
            from="livingSpace"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="street"
            from="street"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="zipCode"
            from="zipCode"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="type"
            from="type"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="isStudent"
            from="isStudent"
            as="boolean"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="bbrId"
            from="bbrId"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="city"
            from="city"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="floor"
            from="floor"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="apartment"
            from="apartment"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Error next="[[offerError]]">
  </Error>
  <Result key="createDanishHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.amount"
          as="danishContentsMonthlyGross"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.currency"
          as="danishContentsMonthlyGrossCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.amount"
          as="danishContentsMonthlyNet"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.currency"
          as="danishContentsMonthlyNetCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.amount"
          as="danishContentsMonthlyDiscount"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.currency"
          as="danishContentsMonthlyDiscountCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishAccidentQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.amount"
          as="danishAccidentMonthlyGross"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishAccidentQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.currency"
          as="danishAccidentMonthlyGrossCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishAccidentQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.amount"
          as="danishAccidentMonthlyNet"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishAccidentQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.currency"
          as="danishAccidentMonthlyNetCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishAccidentQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.amount"
          as="danishAccidentMonthlyDiscount"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishAccidentQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.currency"
          as="danishAccidentMonthlyDiscountCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.amount"
          as="danishTravelMonthlyGross"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.currency"
          as="danishTravelMonthlyGrossCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.amount"
          as="danishTravelMonthlyNet"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.currency"
          as="danishTravelMonthlyNetCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.amount"
          as="danishTravelMonthlyDiscount"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createDanishTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.currency"
          as="danishTravelMonthlyDiscountCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
</GraphQLApi>
